Class IloOplDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.opl.IloOplDataSource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IloCustomOplDataSource, IloOplDataElements

    public class IloOplDataSource
extends java.lang.Object
    Provide data for an OPL model. This class represents a source from which an OPL model can read data. Refer also to the Interfaces User's Manual.
